Requirements
------------

* Python 3.7+
* aiohttp
* elasticsearch
* inflection

Installation
------------

..

    pip install git+https://github.com/pcdshub/archstats


Running the Tests
-----------------
::

  $ pip install -r dev-requirements.txt
  $ pytest -vv


